definition: to succeed/to finish/to complete/to accomplish/to become/to turn into/to be all right/OK!/one tenth

sentences.english: I only honoured my promise to your father.
sentences.chinese: 我只不過完成了我對你父親的承諾。

sentences.english: It's proving very difficult to peg him down to a definite date for completion.
sentences.chinese: 要規定他限期完成確是十分困難的。

sentences.english: When finished with the list, click OK then close out of Local Group Policy Editor.
sentences.chinese: 完成列表後，點擊確定並關閉本地組策略編輯器。

sentences.english: They will expect a career growth and a magnificent actualization of a number of projects.
sentences.chinese: 他們會預期到職業的成長，一些項目會漂亮的完成。

sentences.english: If I have enought money, I will make a journey around the world.
sentences.chinese: 如果我有足夠的資金，我將完成一次環球旅行。

sentences.english: Most global transactions are carried out by a letter of credit (LC).
sentences.chinese: 大多數全球交易都是通過信用證白勺方式完成。

sentences.english: Polio eradication is one of our most important areas of unfinished business.
sentences.chinese: 根除脊髓灰質炎是我們未完成工作的最重要領域之一。

sentences.english: Only humping yourself can you hope to finish your work in time.
sentences.chinese: 只有加把勁幹，你纔有希望按時完成任務。

sentences.english: How could you have handled it differently?
sentences.chinese: 你能以不同的方式完成它麼？

sentences.english: Major non-conformities should require on-site verification within 80 days.
sentences.chinese: 嚴重不符合項應該要求在80天內完成現場驗證工作。

sentences.english: Pull off a successful 4-point play with any player, in a non-simulated game.
sentences.chinese: 非模擬模式比賽，使用任意球員完成四分打。

sentences.english: Research will need to be done for each power point video presentation.
sentences.chinese: 研究將需要爲每個電源點的視頻演示完成。

sentences.english: I finished my job about editing the contest question about biology today.
sentences.chinese: 今天，我已經完成關於生物競賽題的編輯整理工作。

sentences.english: Therefore, collectivity design on The Underwater Ship Hull Cleaning Robot is finished.
sentences.chinese: 完成了船體表面清刷機器人的總體設計。

sentences.english: We has carried out systematic studies to characterize the condition inside the shoes in terms of hygienics.
sentences.chinese: 我們在鞋內衛生方面完成了系統研究，並註明了條件。

sentences.english: The negotiating groups have developed consolidated legal text in virtually all negotiating groups.
sentences.chinese: 談判小組在幾乎所有的談判中均已完成法律文本合併。
